    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >照片灵敏度警告：</h2>即使您过去没有癫痫或癫痫发作，也有一小部分人在暴露于某些光线，图案或图像时可能会发作癫痫。<br><br>BITROOM并不是一个关于Max的少年的漫长冒险故事。马克斯是一个普通的小学生，梦想成为一名游戏开发人员，但他没想到这会导致这种后果。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏包含以下游戏元素：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>武器和战斗系统<br></li><li>对话和笔记<br></li><li>挑战敌人<br></li><li>快速时间事件系统</li></ul>以及更多!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/6b1b4bfe469e21614b4f9c511be432c0.poster.avif?t=1670683175\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/6b1b4bfe469e21614b4f9c511be432c0.webm?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/6b1b4bfe469e21614b4f9c511be432c0.mp4?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏风格</h2><br>游戏结合了2d和3d风格。整个环境都是3d风格的，而角色，敌人和互动元素都是2d风格的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/232a6f01fc81447752b298cb51f6728b.poster.avif?t=1670683175\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/232a6f01fc81447752b298cb51f6728b.webm?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/232a6f01fc81447752b298cb51f6728b.mp4?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难以理解情节</h2><br>游戏的情节相当复杂，并不是每个人都能完全了解第一次的情况。建议您仔细研究对话并阅读分散在各个位置的所有注释。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/d2a425655a3b73aa7b28dd2c52383962.poster.avif?t=1670683175\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/d2a425655a3b73aa7b28dd2c52383962.webm?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/d2a425655a3b73aa7b28dd2c52383962.mp4?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难度等级</h2><br>您无法自己选择难度级别，您需要仔细检查所有位置，以了解如果敌人突然将您惊呆了，您将来将如何采取行动。尽量不要绕过其他位置，可能会有很多有用的东西。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/5d86f2b7be434d2ae161e21d94358570.poster.avif?t=1670683175\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/5d86f2b7be434d2ae161e21d94358570.webm?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411660/extras/5d86f2b7be434d2ae161e21d94358570.mp4?t=1670683175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
